TWO WAYS TO COMPILE:

FIRST WAY:
>> pdflatex ./Thesis.tex
>> bibtex Thesis 
>> mpost ./Feynman.mp    %TO GENERATE Feynman DIAGRAMS
>> pdflatex ./Thesis.tex
>> pdflatex ./Thesis.tex
>> makeindex Thesis %TO GENERATE THE INDEX PAGE


SECOND WAY:
USE LaTeXMk WHICH AUTOMATICALLY COMPILES EVERYTHING EVERYTIME A FILE IS UPDATED

>> latexmk -pvc -pdf ./Thesis.tex




